description:
In an interview taped backstage at the Newport Jazz Festival, guitarist John Scofield talks about his creative process as far as composing.

This interview was taped backstage at the 2017 Newport Jazz Festival, where Scofield performed with the supergroup Hudson featuring  Scofield with John Medeski, Larry Grenadier and Jack DeJohnette.  For more information about Scofield, visit www.johnscofield.com 

Interview by Irene Lee. Produced for JazzTimes by Lee Mergner. You can find more videos, plus news, features, reviews and lots more at www.jazztimes.com
title: Guitarist John Scofield on his creative process
